                         Plasma Theory Group (T-15)

                            Theoretical Division

                       Los Alamos National Laboratory


   The Los Alamos Plasma Theory Group devotes its efforts to advancing our
   understanding of nonlinear and linear plasma behavior in laboratory
   fusion experiments and in space and astrophysical settings.


